🚀 Overview
This repository contains my daily solutions to LeetCode problems. The goal is to improve problem-solving skills, strengthen data structures and algorithms (DSA), and maintain consistency in coding practice for technical interview preparation.

🎯 Objectives
Solve at least one problem daily
Build strong foundations in Data Structures & Algorithms
Improve coding efficiency and logical thinking
Prepare for technical interviews and placements

📂 Repository Structure
daily_leetcode/
│
├── Easy/      # Easy level problems
├── Medium/    # Medium level problems
├── Hard/      # Hard level problems
└── README.md

🧠 Topics Covered
Arrays
Strings
Linked Lists
Stacks & Queues
Trees & Graphs
Dynamic Programming
Recursion & Backtracking
Greedy Algorithms

🛠️ Language Used
Python 

💡 Approach
Each solution in this repository includes:
Clean and readable code
Optimized approach (where applicable)
Focus on time and space complexity

Why This Repository?
This repository reflects my consistency, discipline, and continuous learning mindset, which are essential for becoming a strong software engineer.


